title: Anxiety, ADD, & Mental Health (no sex lol)
description:
Lauren gives the play by play from her first anxiety attack around Jeremy, and explains how he handled it. Jeremy shares his story of growing up with ADD. Lauren recounts how Jeremy welcomed in the new year vomiting off the balcony.
